history.content:
Dear Students,
 
Please note the following modified business hours for the EECS department administrative offices.
  • December 18 (Monday): Advising offices closed at 3:30pm for Excellence in Advising Award Ceremony 
  • December 21 (Thursday):  EECS Undergrad Advisors will be in off-campus meetings starting at 11:45am 
  • December 22 (Friday):  CLOSED; staff will be available via email remotely between 9 am and 12 pm only
  • December 23 - January 1:  CLOSED - winter break/shutdown
If you have urgent matters that must be taken care of before the end of next week, please let us know by no later than Tuesday, 12/19, 12 pm.  This will allow us time to plan and take necessary actions as appropriate.
 
Please see post @5750 for information about L&S CS Advising over the next month.
